    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来控制器不直接查数据，而是委托给DeviceDataFetcher。这是为了解耦，控制器专注协调。",
      "elements_involved": [
